'''Lykan Hypersport'''是由成立於2012年的[[黎巴嫩|黎巴嫩]]公司{{link-en|W Motors|W Motors}}所限量生產的跑車，是[[中東地區|中東地區]]所生產的第一個[[超級跑車|超級跑車]]。<ref>{{cite news|last=McCarthy|first=James|title=How the Lykan Hypersport is the last word in luxury|url=http://www.thenational.ae/lifestyle/motoring/how-the-lykan-hypersport-is-the-last-word-in-luxury|accessdate=19 March 2013|newspaper=The National|date=15 February 2013|archive-date=2015-05-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150520023454/http://www.thenational.ae/lifestyle/motoring/how-the-lykan-hypersport-is-the-last-word-in-luxury|dead-url=no}}</ref> W Motors計劃只生產7台車。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.gizmag.com/w-motors-lykan-hypersport/26119 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2015-03-25 |archive-date=2014-02-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140226103936/http://www.gizmag.com/w-motors-lykan-hypersport/26119/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> 第一輛預先生產的Lykan HyperSport於2013年11月的{{link-en|杜拜國際汽車展|Dubai Motor Show}}推出。<ref>{{cite web|title=Lykan HyperSport|url=http://www.wmotors.ae/pressreviews_images/1384265200English%20Press%20Release%20-%20W%20Motors%20Lykan%20HyperSport-%20Dubai%20Motor%20Show.pdf|work=W Motors|date=November 2013|accessdate=18 February 2014|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140226100126/http://www.wmotors.ae/pressreviews_images/1384265200English%20Press%20Release%20-%20W%20Motors%20Lykan%20HyperSport-%20Dubai%20Motor%20Show.pdf|archivedate=2014年2月26日}}</ref>

==世界上最貴的車==
要價340萬{{USD}}的Lykan HyperSport是第三貴的車，僅次於非常稀少的[[藍寶堅尼|藍寶堅尼]] {{Link-en|Veneno|Lamborghini Veneno}}（450萬{{USD}}）、<ref>{{cite web|title=Most expensive cars in the world|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/autos/world-expensive-cars-gallery-1.1296757?pmSlide=1|work=Daily News|accessdate=17 May 2013|archive-date=2015-06-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150626103338/http://www.nydailynews.com/autos/world-expensive-cars-gallery-1.1296757?pmSlide=1|dead-url=no}}</ref>和唯一一輛的[[邁巴赫|邁巴赫]] {{link-en|Maybach Exelero|Maybach Exelero|Exelero}} （800萬{{USD}}）。<ref>{{cite web|title=Rapper pays $8m for one-off Maybach|url=http://www.topgear.com/uk/car-news/maybach-exelero-2011|website=Top Gear|accessdate=26 January 2015|date=4 May 2011|archive-date=2015-06-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150626122452/http://www.topgear.com/uk/car-news/maybach-exelero-2011|dead-url=no}}</ref>Lykan Hypersport的價格比[[布加迪|布加迪]][[布加迪威龍|威龍Supersport]]還高出100萬美元，因此它擁有世上最昂貴的量產車頭銜。

這款車的價格昂貴的原因是其包含的選配。這是第一輛在大燈附有鑽石的車，前燈是由鈦光[[LED|LED]]用220顆[[鑽石|鑽石]]（15[[克拉|克拉]]）所組成的。
買家可以選擇他們想要嵌入大燈其中[[紅寶石|紅寶石]]和鑽石。此外，客戶可以在一系列的紅寶石、鑽石、黃色鑽石或藍寶石之間做選擇用在車輛上。

==性能==
Lykan HyperSport搭載了由[[保時捷|保時捷]]提供的六缸雙渦輪增壓引擎（3746毫升），<ref>{{cite web|title=Car of the week: W Motors Lykan HyperSport|url=http://www.thesundaytimes.co.uk/sto/ingear/cars/article1205108.ece|website=Sunday Times|accessdate=26 January 2015|date=3 February 2013|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303181643/http://www.thesundaytimes.co.uk/sto/ingear/cars/article1205108.ece|dead-url=no}}</ref>輸出馬力最大可達{{convert|552|kW|bhp PS|0|abbr=on}}和 {{convert|960|Nm|kg.m|0|abbr=on}}的峰值扭力。<ref>{{cite web|title=Specification sheet|url=http://www.wmotors.ae/downloads/Lykan%20HyperSport%20Spec%202014.pdf|work=W Motors|accessdate=7 January 2015|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150421013345/http://www.wmotors.ae/downloads/Lykan%20HyperSport%20Spec%202014.pdf|archivedate=2015年4月21日}}</ref> 這輛車聲稱的最高速度有{{convert|385|km/h|mi/h|0|abbr=on}}和{{convert|0|to|100|km/h|abbr=on}} 的加速時間僅需要2.8秒。

